      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and usage. While the engine starts and runs, the car has several cosmetic imperfections including minor dents, paint fading on the hood, and some interior upholstery wear. It is mechanically functional but will likely require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in optimal running shape. This is an honest option for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming project work.",
