    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
