    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2006 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a factory Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically superlative: the double VANOS system has been fully rebuilt, rod bearings replaced with VAC coated bearings, and the rear subframe reinforced with TMS plates for maximum torsional rigidity. Every individual throttle body is perfectly synchronized, delivering linear power to the 3.64:1 M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains tight with zero bushing deflection, and the factory Laguna Seca Blue paint retains its deep luster. This is a turn-key collector piece with no deferred maintenance and a pristine underside.",
